data.description: Welcome home to 3031 Vernon Avenue. This 3-bedroom home has tons of character and charm from the hardwood floors to the wood staircase, decorative fireplace and the beautiful stained-glassed windows in the living room. The kitchen has been updated with new cabinets, countertops, backsplash, flooring and stainless-steel appliances. The bedrooms also have their own character from built-in shelves, to the window seat and ample closet space. Updated bathroom. The furnace/AC was installed in 2019. Storage in the basement. There is a new parking pad in front of the home and a large backyard.
